               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18380129-name-639" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18380129-name-639" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380129-name-639" type="surname" value="GOODBODY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380129-name-639" type="given" value="ELIZABETH"></interp>ELIZABETH GOODBODY</persName>
                  </hi>. I am the wife of James Goodbody, of No.6, Barnsbury-place. I went to my house in Belinda-place, on the 24th of January—the copper was safe then—I have since missed it—(<hi rend="italic">looking of one</hi>)—it was like this one—I cannot swear to it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
